WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:03.429
Good morning, family. I am so excited

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:05.390
to be here with you today. This is how

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.429
it went, the first of the vision: I

00:00:07.439 --> 00:00:09.709
was praying in the spirit, and the Lord

00:00:09.719 --> 00:00:11.470
took me up into the spirit and he showed

00:00:11.480 --> 00:00:13.150
me all this stuff,

00:00:13.150 --> 00:00:13.160
what’s

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.430
coming. I wanted to

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:18.150
start it out like this: there

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:21.870
was a massive python.

00:00:21.880 --> 00:00:24.910
This thing was, of course,

00:00:24.920 --> 00:00:27.109
in

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:28.669
the spirit realm whenever this

00:00:28.669 --> 00:00:28.679
was

00:00:28.679 --> 00:00:31.070
happening, but

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:32.709
it had

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:37.350
copper spots all on its back.

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:40.950
On the outer lining of the spot,

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.069
there was black, so it was a

00:00:44.069 --> 00:00:44.079
copper-looking

00:00:44.079 --> 00:00:47.830
color, like a really

00:00:47.830 --> 00:00:47.840
red-dirt

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:51.029
kind of color, then it went

00:00:51.029 --> 00:00:51.039
to

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:53.069
black around it.

00:00:53.079 --> 00:00:57.189
The snake was like a normal python,

00:00:57.199 --> 00:00:59.470
but there were different shades all over

00:00:59.470 --> 00:00:59.480
it.

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:03.910
It had its

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:05.270
mouth open, which I thought was

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:07.550
interesting because it was in a strike

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:11.030
position. When it went over

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:15.510
Louisiana, up through Arkansas

00:01:15.510 --> 00:01:15.520
and

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:17.910
Missouri, and wrapped

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:22.510
around America, it pulled tight. Then

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:25.990
the Lord showed me President Biden.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.789
President Biden was standing in the Oval

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:31.069
Office, looking out where

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:34.789
Marine One, the helicopter, goes

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:36.429
right there in the front. He was

00:01:36.439 --> 00:01:38.990
looking out the window, and he was

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.590
in a

00:01:42.590 --> 00:01:42.600
daze.

00:01:42.600 --> 00:01:45.310
He had brain fog really bad

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:47.590
is what I could see. His eyes were kind

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:50.870
of glassy and he was just staring,

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:52.789
looking out over the yard.

00:01:52.799 --> 00:01:54.990
Then this is very interesting: I could

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.789
see seasons come before him as he's

00:01:58.799 --> 00:02:01.069
looking. I could see fall; there

00:02:01.069 --> 00:02:01.079
were

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:03.469
trees in the front and I could see the

00:02:03.479 --> 00:02:06.149
leaves change. Then I could see snow

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:09.910
falling, I could see spring come again

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:11.790
and the trees were budding out, then I

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:15.150
could see the summer and the

00:02:15.160 --> 00:02:17.630
full leafing of the trees. It was all

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:20.030
in this vision that I’m looking into the

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:22.830
spirit; I could just see the trees and the

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:25.790
seasons change in front of him, and

00:02:25.790 --> 00:02:25.800
he’s

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:28.710
just staring in one place, looking out

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:30.470
the window

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.830
in a daze, always looking out this

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:36.670
window. So the Lord showed this to me.

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:40.750
Then the Lord showed me another snake,

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.430
but this snake, of course, is not as big

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:43.949
as the one that came out of the Gulf of

00:02:43.959 --> 00:02:47.710
Mexico. This one was wrapped around his

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:49.790
whole entire body and it was thick.

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:51.630
It was a humongous, thick-looking snake,

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:53.589
and it was black.

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:55.949
It was wrapped around

00:02:55.959 --> 00:02:59.110
his mind

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:01.270
and it was turned and

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:04.030
speaking into his ear,

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:06.350
whispering. I could see the snake's

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:09.110
forked tongue speaking into

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:13.430
his ear. He was trying to control

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:17.110
this snake; it was giving him a source of

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:20.869
power, it was a demonic influence, but he

00:03:20.879 --> 00:03:22.830
thought he was controlling the snake, but

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:25.110
the snake was controlling him. The

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.830
only way I could

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.910
try to give you a picture—remember in

00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:31.030
The Jungle Book, the Disney cartoon,

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:33.110
that snake that would

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:36.550
try to use his eyes to do hypnosis on

00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:36.560
Mowgli,

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:39.710
the little boy?

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:41.949
It was trying to control him through

00:03:41.959 --> 00:03:45.429
brain control. This snake was

00:03:48.280 --> 00:03:51.429
controlling the president's mind through

00:03:51.439 --> 00:03:53.550
a demonic influence because it was

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:57.470
demonic. Then I see behind that

00:03:57.480 --> 00:04:00.470
snake and I see one of our old

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:02.830
presidents, and he was dressed in solid

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:05.830
black. Then I see another person,

00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:05.840
who

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:08.270
was a white man, and I do not know

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:10.550
who this was, but he was taller, a

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:12.509
tall individual, and he was heavy; he

00:04:12.519 --> 00:04:15.190
looked almost like he was

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:17.670
overweight. Then I saw a shorter person,

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:21.349
and I believe this was a female.

00:04:21.359 --> 00:04:24.590
You can know who she is: that

00:04:24.590 --> 00:04:24.600
was an

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:26.790
ex-president's

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:30.270
wife, and she ran for president also

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:33.350
at one time and she lost.

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:36.270
I saw these people—there

00:04:36.270 --> 00:04:36.280
were

00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:38.029
three individuals and they were

00:04:38.039 --> 00:04:39.950
influencing. The Lord showed me as I was

00:04:39.960 --> 00:04:41.550
praying

00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:41.560
over

00:04:41.560 --> 00:04:43.150
this: there was darkness right

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:46.510
here. I had a standing

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:49.110
front man or front woman, and they

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.870
had an earpiece in. I was just in my

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:53.189
basement in my sweats looking through

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:55.830
the stuff, and then I could sort of

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:58.790
deliver the lines, but somebody else was

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:01.629
doing all the talking and ceremony.

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:03.990
I'd be fine with that.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:07.430
Now the Lord took me in the vision

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:11.909
and he showed me New York City. I saw

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:15.150
these two buildings standing by

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:20.590
themselves. All of a sudden

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:25.990
those buildings went, and I saw how I

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.790
know it wasn't like 9/11 because

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:31.430
this was

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:34.550
coming from the inside out. I could

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:38.469
see fire, I could see smoke, I could see

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.830
the pressure from

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:45.390
the blast coming out of the

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:48.110
glass windows, and it went all the way

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:50.830
down. All of a sudden these

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:53.990
massive buildings started

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.670
falling. I could see them all fall

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:58.710
and I could see the

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:00.950
smoke and all the debris; it looked like

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:03.350
cauliflower going all throughout the air.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.230
If you could remember back in 9/11

00:06:05.240 --> 00:06:06.749
whenever that all happened, how

00:06:06.759 --> 00:06:08.749
those fell, that's what that looked like.

00:06:08.759 --> 00:06:10.790
I could see two buildings for sure,

00:06:10.790 --> 00:06:10.800
maybe

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:13.070
a third one; I believe there

00:06:13.070 --> 00:06:13.080
were

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:15.070
three buildings that were involved

00:06:15.070 --> 00:06:15.080
altogether.

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:17.670
When this happened, it shot

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:19.830
debris everywhere.

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:22.670
Whenever I was taken out in the

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:24.469
spirit and I was hovering above, I

00:06:24.479 --> 00:06:26.550
could see all the states. I told you

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:30.589
there was like a gray film all over from

00:06:30.599 --> 00:06:33.950
Arkansas over; it looked similar to

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:36.629
fallout, like soot. I don't know, but it

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:40.189
was thick, almost like

00:06:40.199 --> 00:06:42.950
a substance like ash.

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.629
That's the only way I can tell you: it

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:47.990
looked like ash. There was gray ash on

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:51.270
those states. That's how I'm going to

00:06:51.280 --> 00:06:53.909
describe it. I don't know how

00:06:53.909 --> 00:06:53.919
else,

00:06:53.919 --> 00:06:56.550
because it seemed lumpy, like

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:03.869
fireplace ash on those

00:07:03.879 --> 00:07:08.390
states. It was all from Arkansas over that

00:07:08.390 --> 00:07:08.400
I

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:11.950
saw

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:11.960
this.

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:14.990
Then I could see

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:17.950
a

00:07:17.960 --> 00:07:21.270
humongous mushroom cloud out of New York. I don't

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.029
know what that was, but it didn't have

00:07:23.039 --> 00:07:25.550
anything to do with this; these were two

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:27.510
separate things the Lord was showing me

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:29.710
at this time. I could see

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:31.909
those buildings that were

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:34.990
completely gone, and I believe I know

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:37.150
which buildings they are, but

00:07:37.150 --> 00:07:37.160
I’m

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:39.070
never going to say

00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:41.629
something prophetically that I've seen

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:44.070
and just guess. I saw these buildings, and I

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:48.309
believe it causes a complete

00:07:48.319 --> 00:07:50.189
shutdown of our

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:52.990
economy, a shutdown of everything, because

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:55.149
we're attacked within. There was

00:07:55.159 --> 00:07:56.869
something inside of them to cause the

00:07:56.879 --> 00:08:01.029
pressure to go off.

00:08:01.039 --> 00:08:04.270
Now the Lord tells me to focus and he

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:09.990
shows me two men.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.670
I saw a man that I believe is

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:16.469
the president of a country, and I

00:08:16.479 --> 00:08:19.350
saw another president of a

00:08:19.350 --> 00:08:19.360
country—prime

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:22.830
minister, I think—and they were

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:26.029
participating in a homosexual

00:08:26.039 --> 00:08:29.070
relationship. He was painting his

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:32.389
face, he had lipstick on, he had

00:08:32.399 --> 00:08:35.269
this blue underneath his eyes, and he was

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:38.829
dressed similar to a clown, which I don't

00:08:38.839 --> 00:08:40.269
understand, I'm just telling you

00:08:40.279 --> 00:08:43.550
what I saw. But these two men—one from

00:08:43.560 --> 00:08:45.870
overseas and one not too far from

00:08:45.870 --> 00:08:45.880
here—were

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:47.829
engaging in a

00:08:47.839 --> 00:08:50.190
relationship. I thought that was

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:51.630
very strange.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:57.949
Now I'm going to go

00:08:57.959 --> 00:09:01.030
to what I heard from the Spirit of

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:04.430
the Lord. He started

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:07.630
saying, 'The king from the north and

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:10.470
the kings from the east are

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:13.069
devising a plan against the United

00:09:13.069 --> 00:09:13.079
States.'I

00:09:13.079 --> 00:09:16.949
saw Vladimir Putin and Xi

00:09:16.949 --> 00:09:16.959
Jinping

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:20.230
having a meeting in Saudi Arabia for the

00:09:20.230 --> 00:09:20.240
BRICS

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:23.110
nations. I saw

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:25.750
the man that's over Saudi Arabia,

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:28.150
the prince of Saudi Arabia; he

00:09:28.160 --> 00:09:31.030
started devising a plan, and it was all

00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:33.230
his idea. The Lord was showing me this was his idea.

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:38.310
He said, 'I will put

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:42.350
America under my boot,'and I saw the heel of a boot.

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:45.710
I saw him put

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:48.990
his heel down on America, devising

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:51.310
a plan against us because he could not

00:09:51.320 --> 00:09:53.790
stand Joe Biden. Then I could see Joe

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:57.230
Biden, and there was no leadership over

00:09:57.240 --> 00:10:00.030
America; it was vulnerable

00:10:00.040 --> 00:10:02.509
because of no leadership. That's

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:05.030
when I saw the antichrist spirit and I

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:09.509
saw the

00:10:09.519 --> 00:10:11.990
dark cloud that had lightning all in it.

00:10:11.990 --> 00:10:12.000
It

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:14.550
was

00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:17.750
fierce lightning. The Lord

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:22.069
said, 'Who will stand for America? Who will

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:24.910
stand in the gap for America

00:10:24.910 --> 00:10:24.920
and

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:27.069
intercede?'That's

00:10:27.069 --> 00:10:27.079
when

00:10:27.079 --> 00:10:28.550
the Lord showed me

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:30.350
Jesus standing

00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:32.990
over America pleading for the people to

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.710
intercede for America because of what

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:39.030
was coming. I could see

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:40.990
the antichrist

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:43.230
agenda was getting ready to hover and

00:10:43.240 --> 00:10:45.550
come over America even greater because

00:10:45.560 --> 00:10:49.150
there was no leadership over America. I

00:10:49.160 --> 00:10:51.910
could see the covering that was over

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:55.230
America; it was almost like

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:57.670
we were a sitting duck.

00:11:02.639 --> 00:11:04.949
It was vulnerable. Then the Lord

00:11:04.959 --> 00:11:07.509
took me in the spirit and I saw Israel

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:11.350
and Syria. I could see Iran

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:13.430
devising a plan, and they were

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:15.670
communicating with Syria and they were

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:20.670
sending stuff secretly to Syria.

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:23.590
I saw men coming out of Syria that

00:11:23.590 --> 00:11:23.600
looked

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:27.310
like ants; there were so many men

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:30.110
coming out of Syria, marching in a

00:11:30.120 --> 00:11:32.470
line like soldiers marching.

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:34.389
But they looked like

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:36.670
ants, and I could see they were red.

00:11:36.670 --> 00:11:36.680
That

00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:38.150
was very

00:11:38.150 --> 00:11:38.160
interesting—I

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:40.430
don't understand

00:11:40.430 --> 00:11:40.440
that—but

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:43.550
these men were red and they had

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:45.350
their guns and they were marching

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:46.949
against

00:11:46.959 --> 00:11:49.629
Israel. There were so many of them

00:11:49.639 --> 00:11:52.030
that they were all in single-file lines

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:54.150
going at Israel.

00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:56.710
I saw a great war

00:11:56.720 --> 00:11:59.750
breaking out in Israel,

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:03.030
coming out of Syria. This

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:08.310
attack was so—I saw stress on

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.269
Benjamin Netanyahu, and that's when the

00:12:10.279 --> 00:12:12.190
Lord said, 'Pray for Israel, pray for the

00:12:12.200 --> 00:12:14.269
peace of

00:12:14.269 --> 00:12:14.279
Jerusalem.'I

00:12:14.279 --> 00:12:17.389
saw Benjamin

00:12:17.389 --> 00:12:17.399
Netanyahu—he

00:12:17.399 --> 00:12:19.509
wasn't worried, but I could

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:21.189
see he was sweating a little bit,

00:12:21.199 --> 00:12:22.990
like he was concerned

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:23.000
that

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:25.750
this is going to be a major ordeal.

00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:27.710
This isn't just a couple of rockets

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:30.629
shooting in; this is an all-out war.

00:12:30.639 --> 00:12:33.150
Now I'm going to go back to what

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:37.389
I saw in Saudi Arabia. I could see

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:39.829
this prince of Saudi Arabia

00:12:39.829 --> 00:12:39.839
saying,

00:12:39.839 --> 00:12:44.629
'I'm going to put my boot down on

00:12:44.629 --> 00:12:44.639
America.'He

00:12:44.639 --> 00:12:46.910
had a plan

00:12:46.920 --> 00:12:49.189
because he was against

00:12:49.199 --> 00:12:53.430
Joe Biden. I could see him

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:56.509
devising a plan with Russia

00:12:56.519 --> 00:13:00.509
and China and they were making the

00:13:00.519 --> 00:13:03.389
currency for the BRICS nations, and they

00:13:03.399 --> 00:13:04.829
were going

00:13:04.839 --> 00:13:06.870
to destroy the dollar.

00:13:06.880 --> 00:13:08.829
Suddenly

00:13:08.839 --> 00:13:11.069
I saw it was like one of

